						               													<description>The recently discovered underground continent of Potu is swarming with adventurers after its treasure and secrets, and you're one of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The continent of Potu is made of up location cards in offset rows. Each round characters simply choose whether they'll go up or down when going into the next row of cards. If you end up in a location by yourself you're sure to get it, but if you land on the same card as other adventurer's you'll have to fight to see who gets the treasure. You'll need to avoid fruitless battles and use your skills to your advantage to get the most treasure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Of course each character has something that makes them different, whether that's the Robot who can plan ahead for battles, the Black Cat who can go not just up or down but anywhere, the Professor who gets an extra boost in discoveries, or any of the other characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you come back with the riches of Potu?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
